articles.title: Who Is Rose Hanbury? Prince William Affair Rumor, Explained - The Cut
articles.description: All manner of conspiracy theories about Kate Middleton’s whereabouts have been whispered in the British tabloids and screamed on TikTok. Including Prince William’s rumored affair with the Marchioness of Cholmondeley. Let’s review.
